application_type_full: Outline planning permission: All matters reserved
description: Hybrid application for a phased estate regeneration development of the site comprising a maximum of 102,375 sqm (GIA) of floorspace; up to 89,875 sqm (GIA) as an outline permission (the Outline Component) and full planning permission for Phase A comprising 12,500 sqm (GIA) of residential development (the Detailed Component). The Detailed Component proposes erection of a building up to 13 storeys in height to provide 117 new homes (Use Class C3), together with access, servicing, car parking, cycle parking, cycle storage, plant, play and open space and landscaping. The Outline Component (all matters reserved) for: demolition of all buildings and structures, up to 1280 sqm (GIA) of flexible Commercial / Community Floorspace (Use Class E / F2), up to 80,785 sqm (GIA) of Residential Floorspace (Use Class C3) comprising up to 850 homes, up to 2,550 sqm (GIA) of Plant, up to 5,260 sqm (GIA) of Podium Car Parking, open spaces, landscaping, public realm and other associated and ancillary work.
